quran[29]{c,v,t}:
  70,11,"though they are shown each other. The criminal wishes he could be redeemed from the punishment <span class=""h"">of that day<sup foot_note=""81367"" class=""qiraat"">1</sup> </span>by sacrificing his children"
  70,12,"and his female companion and his brother"
  70,13,"and his kinsfolk who shelter him"
  70,14,"and everyone on earth, so it would then save him."
  70,15,"But no! It is a raging fire"
  70,16,"<span class=""h"">that strips<sup foot_note=""81368"" class=""qiraat"">1</sup> </span>away the scalps,"
  70,17,"inviting the one who had retreated and turned away{1}",footnotes:1:This may mean ‘turned away from the truth’.
  70,18,"and accumulated<i class=""s"">(wealth) </i>and hoarded."
  70,19,"Indeed, man was created fretful:"
  70,20,"when touched by adversity he is impatient,"
  70,21,"and when touched by good he is ungenerous;"
  70,22,"except the prayerful<a class=""sup""><sup>pl </sup></a>"
  70,23,"who are{1}constant at their prayers;",footnotes:1:A grammatical shift from singular to plural.
  70,24,"and those in whose wealth is a rightfully acknowledged share"
  70,25,"for the asker and the deprived;"
  70,26,"and those who believe in the Day of Recompense;"
  70,27,"and those who fear their Lord’s punishment—"
  70,28,"indeed, none can feel secure from their Lord’s punishment;"
  70,29,"and those who preserve their private parts{1},",footnotes:1:A metaphor for maintaining chastity.
  70,30,"except from their spouses or those whom they rightfully possess—for then they are indeed not blameworthy."
  70,31,"But whoever seeks to go beyond that, then those are the transgressors;"
  70,32,"and those who are faithful to <span class=""h"">their trusts<sup foot_note=""81372"" class=""qiraat"">1</sup> </span>and their covenant;"
  70,33,"and those who stand by <span class=""h"">their testimonies<sup foot_note=""81373"" class=""qiraat"">1</sup> </span>;"
  70,34,"and those who preserve their prayers—"
  70,35,"those are honored in Gardens<i class=""s"">(of Paradise) </i>."
  70,36,"So what is with those who have denied, craning their necks towards you<a class=""sup""><sup>sg </sup></a>,"
  70,37,"from the right and from the left, banding together?"
  70,38,"Does every one of them ardently hope to be entered into a Garden of Bliss?"
  70,39,"But no! Indeed, We created them from what they know."
